  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a 20-foot-radius Sphere of fog centered on a point within range. The sphere spreads around corners, and its area is heavily obscured. It lasts for the Duration or until a wind of moderate or greater speed (at least 10 miles per hour) disperses it.</p>\n<p><h3>At Higher Levels</h3> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the radius of the fog increases by 20 feet for each slot level above 1st.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell Lists.</strong> Druid, Ranger, Sorcerer, Wizard</p>",
